Parameters:

  • marked_genes (sequence of str or None) ‚Äì a set of genes/genomic features to be highlighted on the pathway graph. The gene ID type of those genes should match the parameter gene_id_type.

  • gene_id_type ‚Äì the identifier type you want to use when displaying genes in the graph (for example: ‚ÄòUniProtKB‚Äô, ‚ÄòWormBase‚Äô, ‚ÄòRNACentral‚Äô, ‚ÄòEntrez Gene ID‚Äô). :type gene_id_type: str or ‚Äòauto‚Äô (default=‚Äôauto‚Äô)

  • title (str or 'auto' (default='auto')) ‚Äì plot title.

  • ylabel (str (default="$log_2$(Fold Enrichment)")) ‚Äì plot y-axis label.

  • graph_format ('pdf', 'png', 'svg', or 'none' (default='none')) ‚Äì if graph_format is not ‚Äònone‚Äô, the ontology graph will additonally be generated in the specified file format.
